---
title: Seared Duck in Cranberry-Wine Reduction with Maple Brussels Sprouts and Creamy Smashed Potatoes
description: Juicy duck breasts are seared until the skin is crispy and golden-brown, then drizzled with mouthwatering cranberry pan sauce. The roasted maple Brussels sprouts complement these flavours perfectly, and creamy mash finishes off a luxurious meal!
